author: Deva Dalporto
title: Here's Why Moms Yell
text:
Deva Dalporto MyLifeSuckers 
Ever wonder why moms yell so much? Maybe it has something to do with the fact that we repeat ourselves 400,000 times a day. When you have to ask someone to put on their shoes again and again and AGAIN, you’re bound to lose your sh*t. Enjoy my collab with the awesome Mandi Castle . And don’t forget to subscribe to my YouTube channel for more funny videos every Tuesday! xo, Deva More:
